{"tid":499477,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉性侵少女 共和黨州議員吞槍自殺","createTime":"2017-12-15T00:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T04:30:04.000Z","uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed121b00283c2afcc0b86b505315da17bb2965d","tid":499477,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T00:21:18.000Z","msg":"【#MeToo風暴】涉性侵少女 共和黨州議員吞槍自殺<br />\n即時國際  2017-12-14 20:04:32 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n(美聯社)<br />\n<br />\n美國肯塔基州共和黨州議員周一被指曾在寓所地下室性侵犯一名少女，他周三於社交網發文後，晚上被人發現中彈身亡，驗屍官指他很可能吞槍自殺，終年57歲。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜（Dan Johnson）的屍體周三晚被人發現，驗屍官指他將車泊在一處偏遠地區，並說：「這很可能是自殺」，會於周四上午進行解剖確定死因。<br />\n<br />\n去年當選州議員的約翰遜，周一遭肯塔基州調查報告中心（Center for Investigative Reporting）揭發，稱他於2013年曾在家中的地下室性侵犯一名少女。報道指受害人當年曾報警，但警方調查後沒有起訴約翰遜，最後更結案了事。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜周二在教會舉行記者會否認指控，至周三下午5時左右，他在faceboook留言籲外界照顧自己的妻子，稱「創傷後壓力症候群（PTSD）是一種會奪取我性命的疾病」，有關留言後來已被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171214/57579545\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171214%2F57579545&d=QityVE64U90TG%2BhHdk7iNcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=77519385\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171214%2F57579545&h=2f32666b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171214/57579545</a>"},{"pid":"703390464510f442c0578a68da4c7a42e5a34ec8","tid":499477,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T00:36:35.000Z","msg":"部分會員:佢一定受好大侮辱先會自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a75d5b2826e52a7bc7ba9a102a3e8b5b0b2a553","tid":499477,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T00:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>部分會員:佢一定受好大侮辱先會自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀  好人好姐洗自殺？<br />\n明顯畏罪"},{"pid":"3057e0304e0a85f97d72860a6726a832b11373a9","tid":499477,"uid":30368,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T01:03:02.000Z","msg":"以前就覺得個個都畏罪自殺<br />\n但而家我覺得會自殺既多數都係好人黎，佢應該無做過"},{"pid":"24fd3a53922c4cf7802534216fb4593d2db5eb17","tid":499477,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:23:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7028e83843209c4d5c63c187116ec398004bbfd","tid":499477,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:28:45.000Z","msg":"#METOO 第一滴血<br />\n<br />\n無成本玩死人, 點解唔做?"},{"pid":"af6fe81f24711c824af9ec2da38d4e66935932c6","tid":499477,"uid":61050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:30:04.000Z","msg":"仲以為係Ray Moore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}